These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, funk
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of funk is not to the right of the fan of funk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | d&b |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, satire
1. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | musical |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | goldfish | hedgehog |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, train
1. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | scooter | train |

 #################################
 
